hr.fer.zemris.java.tecaj.hw07.shell

Interface Environment

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EnvironmentImpl

    public interface Environment
    Defines a shell environment. It has capabilities of storing ShellCommands, writing to output stream, reading input stream and stores symbols for multiline input and shell prompt.
    Author:
    Luka Skugor
